 4:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='259646' id='t-259646'>So four, almost five years ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='262691' id='t-262691'>Proposition 8, the great marriage equality debate,</span>
