<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='299246' id='t-299246'>If this was a war with two disparate sides,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='302364' id='t-302364'>I, by default, fell on team gay,</span>
