 5:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='335592' id='t-335592'>I had spent a year photographing this new generation of girls, much like myself,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340743' id='t-340743'>who fell kind of between-the-lines --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='342409' id='t-342409'>girls who skateboarded but did it in lacy underwear,</span>
