<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='387912' id='t-387912'>I was not an activist.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='389446' id='t-389446'>I wave no flags in my own life.</span>
