 9:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='580043' id='t-580043'>It's when you don't have to think about it, simple as that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583663' id='t-583663'>The fight for equal rights is not just about gay marriage.</span>
