<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='717069' id='t-717069'>So after traveling and talking to people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720748' id='t-720748'>in places like Oklahoma or small-town Texas,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='724596' id='t-724596'>we found evidence that the initial premise was dead on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='728131' id='t-728131'>Visibility really is key.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730017' id='t-730017'>Familiarity really is the gateway drug to empathy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733280' id='t-733280'>Once an issue pops up in your own backyard or amongst your own family,</span>
